    <title>Hexo+New+Gitalk搭建个人博客</title>
    <url>/2020/01/17/1/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Hexo"><a href="#Hexo" class="headerlink" title="Hexo"></a>Hexo</h1><h1 id="Next"><a href="#Next" class="headerlink" title="Next"></a>Next</h1><h1 id="Gitalk"><a href="#Gitalk" class="headerlink" title="Gitalk"></a>Gitalk</h1><h1 id="坑"><a href="#坑" class="headerlink" title="坑"></a>坑</h1><h2 id="为什么评论没有用Gitment"><a href="#为什么评论没有用Gitment" class="headerlink" title="为什么评论没有用Gitment"></a>为什么评论没有用Gitment</h2><p>吃着火锅唱着歌，部署到一半发现gitment停止更新了。但是因为改了好多东西，重新clone了一遍next主题，只不过是从头再来。</p>
<h2 id="新建页面-categories-20-报错"><a href="#新建页面-categories-20-报错" class="headerlink" title="新建页面/categories/%20/报错"></a>新建页面<code>/categories/%20/</code>报错</h2><p>新建page的方法是一样的，无论是关于、标签、分类、留言板，但是在修改<code>hexo\_config.yml</code>时，需要把<code>/</code>和<code>||</code>之间的空格删掉才会生效，算是next的娘胎病。<br>原来是：</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">home:</span> <span class="string">/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">home</span>  <span class="string">//首页</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">about:</span> <span class="string">/about/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">user</span>  <span class="string">//关于</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">tags:</span> <span class="string">/tags/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">tags</span>  <span class="string">//标签</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="string">/categories/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">th</span>   <span class="string">//分类</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">archives:</span> <span class="string">/archives/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">archive</span> <span class="string">//归档</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>修改后：</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">home:</span> <span class="string">/||</span> <span class="string">home</span>  <span class="string">//首页</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">about:</span> <span class="string">/about/||</span> <span class="string">user</span>  <span class="string">//关于</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">tags:</span> <span class="string">/tags/||</span> <span class="string">tags</span>  <span class="string">//标签</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="string">/categories/||</span> <span class="string">th</span>   <span class="string">//分类</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">archives:</span> <span class="string">/archives/||</span> <span class="string">archive</span> <span class="string">//归档</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="hexo预览正常上传显示404"><a href="#hexo预览正常上传显示404" class="headerlink" title="hexo预览正常上传显示404"></a>hexo预览正常上传显示404</h2><p>建立repo时，<code>username</code>是包括<code>.github.io</code>的，如果确认没问题，就多刷新几遍。</p>
<h2 id="hexo-d部署不成功"><a href="#hexo-d部署不成功" class="headerlink" title="hexo d部署不成功"></a>hexo d部署不成功</h2><p>先<code>hexo clean</code>再<code>hexo d</code></p>
<h2 id="标题中文显示乱码"><a href="#标题中文显示乱码" class="headerlink" title="标题中文显示乱码"></a>标题中文显示乱码</h2><p><code>hexo\_config.yml</code>里语言设置为zh-Hans，并修改<code>hexo\_config.yml</code>和<code>hexo\themes\next\_config.yml</code>编码方式为UTF-8。</p>
<h2 id="新建文章时的模板"><a href="#新建文章时的模板" class="headerlink" title="新建文章时的模板"></a>新建文章时的模板</h2><p>在<code>hexo new xxx</code>之后默认使用的模板修改<code>hexo\scaffolds\post.md</code><br>目前使用的模板如下，但是置顶和密码还没有做设置。</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">&#123;&#123;</span> <span class="string">title</span> <span class="string">&#125;&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="string">&#123;&#123;</span> <span class="string">date</span> <span class="string">&#125;&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">tags:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">AAA</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">BBB</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">categories:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">permalink:</span> <span class="number">01</span>  <span class="comment">#文章链接，有默认值</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">top:</span> <span class="number">0</span>              <span class="comment">#置顶优先级</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">password:</span>      <span class="comment">#密码保护</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="配置gitalk无法初始化跳转到首页"><a href="#配置gitalk无法初始化跳转到首页" class="headerlink" title="配置gitalk无法初始化跳转到首页"></a>配置gitalk无法初始化跳转到首页</h2><p>在配置gitalk实际上用的是某一个repo的issue功能，我新建了一个<code>nwrepo</code>专门存放评论，在填写OAuth的时候和配置的时候就要注意，以免点了初始化就跳转到首页。<br>在[OAuth Apps]: <a href="https://github.com/settings/developers" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/settings/developers</a> 中填写<code>Authorization callback URL</code>的时候，要填写<code>https://</code>开头的访问地址，而不是github里面那一整个repo的地址。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Application name</span><br><span class="line">1111111</span><br><span class="line">Homepage URL</span><br><span class="line">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;xxxx.github.io</span><br><span class="line">Application description</span><br><span class="line">2222222</span><br><span class="line">Authorization callback URL</span><br><span class="line">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;xxxx.github.io</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在<code>hexo\themes\next\_config.yml</code>中把存储评论的新repo填进去。</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">gitalk:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">githubID:</span> <span class="string">xxxx</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">nwrepo</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">ClientID:</span> <span class="string">looooooooooooooooooooong</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">ClientSecret:</span> <span class="string">loooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooong</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">adminUser:</span> <span class="string">xxxx</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">distractionFreeMode:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>这样所有的评论都会在<code>nwrepo</code>的这个issue里看到。</p>
<h2 id="配置gitalk某些页面禁用评论框"><a href="#配置gitalk某些页面禁用评论框" class="headerlink" title="配置gitalk某些页面禁用评论框"></a>配置gitalk某些页面禁用评论框</h2><p>按照asdfv1929这个大佬的方法配置的，一顿操作之后每页都出现了底下的评论框，但是我在关于页面、标签页面、目录页面都不希望出现评论框，希望评论框出现在某些固定的页面，找到了一个非常复杂的方法在REF里，但是因为要从头改，就放弃了，如果是从头开始部署的可以操作。<br>如果和我一样部署到一半的，需要这个功能的话，可以参考官方给出的方式，在某些固定的页面禁用评论。</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">注意：如果有集成评论服务，页面也会带有评论。</span> <span class="string">若需要关闭的话，请添加字段</span> <span class="string">comments</span> <span class="string">并将值设置为</span> <span class="literal">false</span><span class="string">，如：</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">禁用评论示例</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">标签</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2014</span><span class="number">-12</span><span class="number">-22</span> <span class="number">12</span><span class="string">:39:04</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">"tags"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">comments:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="REF"><a href="#REF" class="headerlink" title="REF"></a>REF</h1><h2 id="Hexo搭建"><a href="#Hexo搭建" class="headerlink" title="Hexo搭建"></a>Hexo搭建</h2><h2 id="Next美化"><a href="#Next美化" class="headerlink" title="Next美化"></a>Next美化</h2><h2 id="Gitalk评论"><a href="#Gitalk评论" class="headerlink" title="Gitalk评论"></a>Gitalk评论</h2><h2 id="坑-1"><a href="#坑-1" class="headerlink" title="坑"></a>坑</h2>]]></content>
